## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date and comprehensive data on UN operations and challenges. Some sources may have inherent biases, and the complexity of international relations means that not all challenges can be fully captured in a single report. Additionally, the dynamic nature of global politics means that new challenges can emerge rapidly, potentially altering the current landscape.